# Metastream.json was generated by:

```js
table = $("#minecraft_items")
data = child => child.children[3].innerText 
id = child => child.children[2].innerText 
name2 = child => {
if(child.children[1].children[2]) {
return child.children[1].children[2].innerText
} else {
return child.children[1].children[1].innerText}
}
getname = child => child.children[1].children[0].innerText 

for(let i = 1 ; i < table.children[0].childElementCount; i++) {
let child = table.children[0].children[i]
  
  item = {
  ImgSrc: image(child),
  FName: getname(child),
	TName: name2(child),
	ID: id(child),
	Data: data(child),
}

	json_stream += JSON.stringify(item)+ "\n"
	console.log(item)
}
```
